name: Rapunzel Disney Princess, Tangled by YeiyeiArt
description:
Rapunzel is a well-known Disney princess. REMEMBER to follow the social networks and ask for your own model. To create the Lora, a meticulously selected and refined DataSet was used to achieve a versatile and flexible model. So that it adapts perfectly to styles and models. It also works in 3D. Use the keyword “(RapunzelWaifu:1)” for greater precision, and I also recommend using the keywords “(dress)” to invoke her characteristic outfit. If you want to change her outfit, I recommend lowering the weight of the Lora between “0.8 - 0.5” for greater flexibility, try it out and have fun. Remember to leave a Review with an image if you liked it and comment!! HAVE FUN :D

Enjoy the model and share your images with the community!!
